      },
      "date": "2018-12-03 22:16:05.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Trevis Autotest2 retesting optional review-ldiskfs-arm session.\n > Requested by Chris Horn because of LU-10073\n\nNote that *optional* test sessions like review-ldiskfs-arm above and review-dne-zfs-part-[34] do not need to pass in order for a patch to land (they are optional because they are newly added and fail too often, but we want to run them a lot to ensure we catch intermittent failures that aren't seen by just a few runs).\n\nOn the other hand, *required* test sessions like review-dne-part-4 DO need to pass in order for a patch to land, so those are the ones that people should pay attention to.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
